	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=88762><span id= >Lady Cylestria</span></a><br><span id=notbold>19 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good [4.40]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>I actually made this one. :)&nbsp;&nbsp;And eventually the picture will be fixed so you can see that, heh.  This isn't a tradeskills site, so please don't ask me to get into all the &quot;how to's&quot; and &quot;where do you's&quot; etc.  This is just the basic: 'wheel and kiln' pottery recipe.<br><br>Put 1 Celestial Essence, 1 Water Flask, 1 Idol Sketch, 1 Imbued Emerald, 1 Vial of Distilled Mana, 1 Sculpting Tool, 1 Gold Bar, and 1 Large Block of Magic Clay in a pottery wheel, combine.<br><br>Fire it with a High Quality Firing Sheet and Divine Crystalline Glaze.<br><br>If you do not know how to get or make some of these components, please follow the links already provided and/or visit www.eqtraders.com, particularly the pottery message board.  <br><br>Please note: This is a &quot;Grandmaster&quot; pottery recipe, trivials well above 200+ possibly a post-250 recipe.  <br><br></p>&nbsp;<br><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br>Cylestria </td></tr>
